        "It is important to complete the full course of antibiotics as prescribed, even if symptoms improve.",
        "Mosquito avoidance strategies, especially during dawn and dusk, and the use of insect repellent."
    ],
    "follow_up": {
        "timing": "1 week after discharge, then 1 month later",
        "conditions": "Return immediately if symptoms worsen, new neurological symptoms develop, or fever persists beyond 48 hours of antibiotic therapy."
